# HTML Form Basics Project

## 📌 Project Overview
This project demonstrates the basic structure and usage of HTML forms. It is designed for beginners to understand how user input is collected using different form elements in HTML.

---

## 📚 What You Will Learn
In this project, you will learn:
- How to create a basic HTML form
- How to use input fields
- How to use labels for better user experience
- How to use different form elements like:
  - Text input
  - Email input
  - Password field
  - Radio buttons
  - Checkboxes
  - Submit button

---

## 🧪 Features of This Project
- Simple and clean HTML form structure
- User input fields for data entry
- Proper use of labels and placeholders
- Beginner-friendly design

